People's Daily commentator: “The 14th Five-Year Plan” gets off to a good start – On studying and implementing the spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference – Xinhua News Agency
Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, December 11th – People’s Daily, December 12th: Commentator’s article: “A Good Start for the 14th Five-Year Plan” – On Studying and Implementing the Spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference
“A good start has been made under the 14th Five-Year Plan,” the Central Economic Work Conference, held from December 8 to 10, highly praised the achievements made in China’s economic and social development over the past year.
General Secretary Xi Jinping delivered an important speech at the meeting, in which he profoundly summarized the economic work of 2021, conducted an in-depth analysis of the current economic situation, and made significant arrangements for the economic work of 2022. This has provided us with a clear direction for our economic efforts next year and the fundamental guidelines necessary to welcome the successful convening of the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
We celebrate with great pomp the centenary of the founding of the Communist Party of China, officially announcing the completion of building a moderately prosperous society in all respects and the achievement of the first centenary goal. We embark on a new journey to comprehensively build a modern socialist country and strive towards the second centenary goal.
We convened the Sixth Plenary Session of the 19th Central Committee of the Party to summarize the major achievements and historical experiences of the Party’s century-long struggle. We adopted the third historical resolution in the Party’s century-long history: “The Resolution of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China on the Major Achievements and Historical Experiences of the Party’s Century-Long Struggle.” This resolution serves as a political declaration for Chinese Communists in the new era to remember their original aspirations and missions, to uphold and develop socialism with Chinese characteristics. It also acts as a guide for using history as a mirror, for forging ahead
Over the past year, the world has experienced major changes unseen in a century, coupled with the global pandemic of COVID-19. The external environment has become increasingly complex and challenging, while the tasks of preventing and controlling the COVID-19 outbreak domestically, as well as promoting economic and social development, have proven to be extremely arduous.
The Party Central Committee, with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core, has adhered to a comprehensive approach that takes into account both domestic and international situations. It has maintained a steady yet progressive working approach, calmly responding to the profound changes of the past century and the global pandemic. The Committee has coordinated efforts between epidemic control and economic and social development, accelerated the establishment of a new development pattern, strengthened the macroeconomic policy framework for cross-cycle regulation, focused on promoting sustainable and healthy economic growth, and made significant strides in reform, opening up, and innovation. As a result, the Party and the country have achieved new and significant accomplishments in
The “14th Five-Year Plan” has gotten off to a good start, and one important aspect of this is that new progress has been made in establishing a new development pattern, with tangible results achieved in high-quality development.
Our country has maintained a leading position globally in terms of economic development and epidemic prevention and control. Its characteristics of strong resilience, significant potential, and ample momentum continue to be evident. The national strategic scientific and technological capabilities have been rapidly enhanced, with numerous major innovations emerging, and the capacity for scientific and technological innovation has continued to improve, leading to new breakthroughs in key core technologies. The resilience of the industrial chain has been strengthened, the volume and quality of foreign trade have increased, and its structure has continued to optimize. New drivers of growth, represented by emerging industries, new business models, and new approaches, are growing stronger. Reform
The achievement of these results is due to the strong leadership of the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core, the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era, and the concerted efforts and hard work of the entire Party and people of all ethnic groups across the country.
Practice has once again proven that the Party’s establishment of Comrade Xi Jinping as the core of the Central Committee and of the entire Party, as well as the establishment of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era as the guiding principle, is of decisive significance for the development of the Party and the country in the new era and for advancing the historical process of the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
With General Secretary Xi Jinping at the core of the Party Central Committee and the entire Party, providing guidance and leadership; with the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era; and with the unity and tenacious efforts of the entire Party and people of all ethnic groups across the country, we are certain to overcome all kinds of difficulties and obstacles. We will create new glories for our era and achieve new historical feats on the new journey of building a modern socialist country in all respects.
Next year, the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China will be held, which is a major event in the political life of the Party and the country.
By promoting the great spirit of party building, adhering to the general approach of seeking progress while maintaining stability, fully, accurately, and comprehensively implementing the new development concepts, accelerating the establishment of a new development pattern, deepening reform and opening up, focusing on innovation-driven development, and striving for high-quality growth, we can ensure that supply-side structural reforms remain the main focus. We must coordinate epidemic prevention and control with economic and social development, balance growth with security, continue to work on the “six stabilities” and “six guarantees,” continuously improve people’s livelihoods, stabilize the macroeconomic situation, and maintain a reasonable range
Let us unite even more closely around the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping at its core, strengthen our “Four Consciousnesses,” firm up our “Four Spheres of Confidence,” and resolutely uphold the “Two Upholds.” We must continuously improve our political judgment, understanding, and execution capabilities. By taking concrete actions, we must ensure that the decisions and arrangements of the Party Central Committee are implemented effectively, and we must push forward the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era.
