In the domestic context, the right-wing advocates for freedom and focus on efficiency and development, while the left-wing emphasizes regulation and places greater importance on fairness and security.
In today’s society, there is a general desire for greater emphasis on fairness. At the same time, with the Sino-US rivalry, a left-leaning stance is inevitable and is likely to continue for many years to come.
